## Directions for changing the menu from jgmenu to openbox ##

Change this code on, or about line 727 of ~/.config/openbox/rc.xml:

        <action name="Execute">
          <command>jgmenu_run</command>
          
to:
          
        <action name="ShowMenu">
          <menu>root-menu</menu>
          
And then press 'Restart' from the menu, or 'openbox --reconfigure' from 
your  terminal.

To check out the current openbox menu without changing the rc.xml file,
use the keybind 'Ctl +Alt + q'
